import style from './Form.module.css'

const Form=(props)=>{
    return(
        <form className={style.containerForm}>
            <section>
            <label htmlFor="user">Username:</label>
            <input type="text"></input>
            </section>
            <section>
            <label htmlFor="password">Password:</label>
            <input type="pasword"></input>
            </section>
            <button>Login</button>
        </form>
    )
}

export default Form
